  "prompt": "Is there a way to sync music to iPhone without iTunes?",
  "response": "Yes, there are several ways to sync music to an iPhone without using iTunes. Here are some popular methods:\n\n1. **Using iCloud Music Library:**\n   - If you have an Apple Music subscription, you can use the iCloud Music Library to sync your music across devices.\n   - Steps:\n     1. Enable iCloud Music Library on your computer (in the Music app on macOS or iTunes on Windows).\n     2. Add your music to the library.\n     3. On your iPhone, go to `Settings > Music` and turn on `Sync Library`.\n     4. Your music should now be available in the Music app on your iPhone.\n\n2. **Using Third-Party Apps:**\n   - Several apps allow you to transfer music to your iPhone without iTunes. Some popular options include:\n     - **VLC for Mobile**: You can use VLC to play media files on your iPhone. You can transfer files using a cloud service or directly through a computer.\n     - **Documents by Readdle**: This app allows you to manage files and transfer music to your iPhone via Wi-Fi or cloud storage.\n     - **iMazing**: A more comprehensive solution that allows you to transfer music, manage your library, and back up your device without iTunes.\n\n3. **Using Cloud Services:**\n   - You can upload your music to cloud storage services like Google Drive, Dropbox, or OneDrive, and then access it on your iPhone.\n   - Steps:\n     1. Upload your music files to your chosen cloud service.\n     2. Download the corresponding app on your iPhone (e.g., Google Drive, Dropbox).\n     3. Download the music files to your iPhone and use a media player app to play them.\n\n4. **Using a USB Drive with Lightning Connector:**\n   - You can use a USB drive with a Lightning connector to transfer music directly to your iPhone.\n   - Steps:\n     1. Copy your music files to the USB drive.\n     2. Connect the USB drive to your iPhone.\n     3. Use the Files app to access the drive and transfer the music to your iPhone.\n\nEach of these methods has its own advantages, so you can choose the one that best fits your needs.",
